cs.DB, cs.GT, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.CC. 

This paper deals with pricing queries against a database, which is a topic closely related to database systems and data management. Therefore, cs.DB is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses pricing algorithms and buyer utility models, which are topics related to game theory (cs.GT) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper proposes approximation algorithms, which are related to algorithms and data structures (cs.DS) and computational complexity (cs.CC).
